item.title: CVE-2020-4920|2024-08-04T08:14:59.189Z -- ibm -- rational%20engineering%20lifecycle%20manager
item.description: IBM Jazz Team Server products are vulnerable to stored cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 191396.
